We have just added this copy of the second, enlarged edition with supplement to our website: https://t.co/minAD3e8E6 https://t.co/rQq4hItSyv

…and it was – as James R. Moore wrote – ‘a monumental achievement – one of the most important reference books to be published in the twentieth century on the culture of science, technology, and medicine’.
